data.description: Your dream home is here! 5 bed, 3 bath + family room on the outskirts of town. Updated kitchen, Spacious backyard with a small fenced off garden area will bring out your green thumb. The large shed has been utilized for wood working along with other hobby passions. RV/Boat parking space is a added bonus! Sellers will pay for a duct cleaning! Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity, call your local real estate agent today to schedule a showing!
